    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Radishes are another vibrant veggie that really compliment corn. If I have one around I dice it the size of the kernals-maybe a little bigger-and mix it in right before service. The bright pink or red of the radish looks so festive nestled in the corn.</></>A trick for removing the corn from the cobb: set your mandoline at the sidest setting and slice away!</p>
