    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>dinner tonight: a handful of fresh arugula, this corn (you may have had your last hurrah 3 months ago, but sunday at the farmer&#8217;s market, the white corn was so sweet and poppy that they had a bowl of fresh, raw kernels out as samples) spooned over the arugula while still hot to just wilt it a bit, and homemade breadcrumbs, toasted in the leftover butter with sage.  soooo good!</p>
    </div>

